78,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:46:41.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"75a5ca61c38b74f12b0e451697b516853ca4c458","tid":288678,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>國際足球協會理事會（IFAB) 建議，修改足球賽例，包括將現時半場45分鐘時長度，縮短為30分鐘，但計時將不會計入球賽因出界或球員受傷等而停頓的時間，措施是希望改善領先球隊「氹波鐘」的情況。<br />\n<br />\n該份名為「Play Fair」的策略性文件，將會在未來數月討論，然後在明年3月提交至周年大會商討，並決定採納那些建議。國際足協理事會技術總監David Elleray表示，該文件是「靜悄悄起革命（a quiet revolution）」。<br />\n<br />\n文件尚提出多項建議，<span style=\"color: red;\">[l包括若罰球被救出，球員不可以補射，而要開球門球</span>，又如將球場大鐘與教練計時手錶連結。</blockquote><br />\n弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n罰球一定係射咩<br />\n斬入去俾龍門掂到唔通唔俾射呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係指12碼。蝗語黎</blockquote><br />\n蝗唔係點球咩</blockquote><br />\n好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾蝗語"},{"pid":"3caa2218a2a3b89cb62949708ed794e18f8d86c7","tid":288678,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"都係解決唔到黑哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14cd431052bfe957c797d392c1db8835e8bd724","tid":288678,"uid":33007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:38:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>直接取消補時轉做停錶咪得 點解要縮埋個時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<br />\n明明無90都有80<br />\n做乜變60<br />\n60根本係場場加時/和</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正正就係有指而家實際嘅比賽時間只有五十幾分鐘;<br />\n人地先建議用用60分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n上屆世界盃實際比賽時間只有55分鐘。"},{"pid":"c6d3cf9ea72a7f8a8eccf7e64d7b6326cccc6596","tid":288678,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:52:42.000Z","msg":"幾時開埋冷氣?"},{"pid":"036e64e5092d09b1382ec1cb26e6c85272cb18c3","tid":288678,"uid":33007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":